-- Rich Jaroslovsky Examines Electronics for Sand and Surf: Video
-- 
-- 2010-06-23T04:20:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/rich-jaroslovsky-examines-electronics-for-sand-and-surf-video.html

          
          
             Bloomberg's Rich Jaroslovsky takes a
look at electronic gadgets that allow consumers to bring their 
digital lives with them as they head for the beach during summer
fun months.  
 Panasonic Corp., Amazon.com Inc., Eastman Kodak Co., 
Qualcomm Inc.,  and Grace Digital Inc. offer some devices that 
might prove useful next to the suntan lotion, folding chair and 
cooler. (Source: Bloomberg)  
